{"tid":716650,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《與神同行》有望加碼兩集變四部曲","createTime":"2018-06-25T12:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T13:45:55.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d9faf88c4509036b41f56e8fb6aeb1e7ce013f5d","tid":716650,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:20:10.000Z","msg":"由河正宇、朱智勛等人主演嘅韓國賣座電影《與神同行》，下集《與神同行：終極審判》將於港韓同步上映，8月1日起喺香港有優先場，9日正式上映。<br />\n<br />\n《與神同行》下集日前公開首段預告片，當戲迷以為今集會係最後一集《與神同行》後，韓國方面就傳來消息，指《與神同行》有望將製作第三至四部，而第三及第四部同樣由金容華導演所執導，亦會同時製作及拍攝，希望於明年底開機，但演出陣容及故事係唔係延續頭兩集內容，一切就未確定。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，《與神同行》製作方今日回應：「目前係希望大過計劃，具體開拍詳情仲未落實，而內容方面都有好多可能性，例如係前傳或衍生作品等。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180625/58360298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F58360298&d=KmpeZqweOkxZceHMK33iMW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a84e686b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F58360298&h=a02931fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180625/58360298</a>"},{"pid":"d84f308776d2344bfa370bb35182bdb066fc115d","tid":716650,"uid":6436,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:42:11.000Z","msg":"睇錯與敵同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616d03ca2ba55ccea338d9892eb4c7f3077b04d4","tid":716650,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:06:31.000Z","msg":"見好就收啦<br />\n唔係集集都有得比你死老母呃眼淚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edbad6088efc35978a4598b6469bc5127e97693","tid":716650,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:07:40.000Z","msg":"有冇咁多扭橋呀"},{"pid":"db23d96f7d3d497ec2f39b56dcec1d0e24167757","tid":716650,"uid":33125,"like":7,"dislike":0